         spec128.[ch],spec16.c,spec48.[ch],spec48_ntsc.c,specplus2a.c,
         specplus2.c,specplus3.[ch],specplus3e.c,spec_se.c,tc2048.c,
         tc2068.[ch],ts2068.c}: factor out common peripheral sets.
