         tc2068.h,ts2068.c},periph.[ch]: move final peripherals into new
         framework. This allows us to kill periph_setup().
20110130 sound.c: ULA book says that MIC only isn't enough to drive the speaker
         as output voltage is below the 1.4v threshold (Fred).
