         just after Fuse starts up on non-Wii platforms (patch #3410841) (Sergio
         Baldov).
20110925 ui/win32/installer/fuse.nsi: windows installer improvements; by
         default, don't register file extensions associated with other programs,
         association with file extensions can be individually enabled, add fuse
         to the OpenWith programs list for known extensions and add .pzx
         extension association (patch #3413548) (Sergio Baldov).
