20111114 unittests/unittests.c: add 48K and +2A/+3 paging unit tests.
20111114 machines/pentagon1024.c: Pentagon1024 does not have 128K-style memory
         paging (as paging is not locked on a write of 0x20 unless the
         secondary port has been written to as well).
20111114 unittests/unittests.c: add Pentagon paging tests.
20111114 unittests/unittests.c: get more test coverage by using
         writeport_internal rather than explicit function calls.
20111114 unittests/unittests.c: add TC2068 paging test.
20111117 unittests/unittests.c: update expected TS2068 contention result after
         TS2068 timing change in libspectrum change r3854.
20111118 unittests/unittests.c: add TC2048 paging test.
20111118 machines/spec_se.c: Spectrum SE does not have 128K-style memory paging
         as "port 0x7ffd" is fully decoded.
20111118 memory.c: assign memory_source_dock and memory_source_exrom.
